data.title: Diva Hamasaki to marry actor Schwarz
data.meta_description: TOKYO, Japan - This undated file photo shows Japanese pop singer Ayumi Hamasaki who her agency said Jan. 1, 2011, will marry Austrian actor Manuel Schwarz.
